Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.98,0:01:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  愛子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.67,0:01:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要開門
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.91,0:01:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？  為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.23,0:01:44.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.93,0:01:47.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就去開了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.40,0:01:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在準備著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.20,0:01:57.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.89,0:02:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了見小愛  我把家裡的事速速了結了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.69,0:02:07.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實…不用勉強來的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.26,0:02:09.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要說的就這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.27,0:02:12.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就坦率的高興點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.99,0:02:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個  是給你的慰勞品
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.72,0:02:17.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…那個是我的毛衣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.99,0:02:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.87,0:02:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比一下尺寸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.25,0:02:25.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿  從後面貼在我背上比比
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.79,0:02:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是很憧憬的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.31,0:02:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你撒什麼嬌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.68,0:02:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.89,0:02:37.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還得開店
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.73,0:02:41.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們很礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.95,0:02:46.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  是不是惹她生氣了啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.22,0:02:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼都沒有做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.20,0:02:54.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  上個休息日  你做什麼事情去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.79,0:02:58.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我代替你去幫她選毛衣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.84,0:03:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.96,0:03:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  一定要好好向她解釋哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.39,0:03:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全是我喜歡的零食
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.33,0:03:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼  像我這種人…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.91,0:03:49.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是我的好朋友  真的是個不錯的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.79,0:03:50.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.08,0:03:57.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.36,0:04:00.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然是真一郎的好朋友的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.11,0:04:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.76,0:04:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請和我交往吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.62,0:04:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小愛  三代吉是個不錯的人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.16,0:04:24.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我保證
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.90,0:04:32.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道  是個好人呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.90,0:04:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.42,0:04:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.96,0:04:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你哭什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.36,0:04:53.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…是個笨蛋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.74,0:05:17.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.69,0:05:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  阿真你回來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.57,0:05:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我的房間裡  不是有本相冊的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.60,0:05:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那個的話被我扔了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.42,0:05:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃？  為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.69,0:05:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種東西  拿著也沒有什麼用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.62,0:05:47.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那張照片
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.37,0:06:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你給小愛打過電話了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.00,0:06:03.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒  那種日子就隨她去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.98,0:06:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人很麻煩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.29,0:06:08.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就正因為那份麻煩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.22,0:06:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「對不起  我太任性了」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.58,0:06:16.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「沒關係  只要是小可愛你的任性的話」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.08,0:06:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯有這樣挺過一切暴風雨  才會孕育出愛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.11,0:06:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  等你也交上女朋友就會明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.16,0:06:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女朋友啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.59,0:06:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說  她怎麼樣？  湯淺比呂美
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.62,0:06:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然拿我開涮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.56,0:06:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近你們關係不錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.66,0:06:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.85,0:06:41.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.58,0:06:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她有別的心上人了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.22,0:06:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我勸那個人和比呂美交往
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.62,0:06:52.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼要做那種事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.50,0:06:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自然而然
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.78,0:06:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白癡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.24,0:07:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比呂美  快攻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.62,0:07:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比呂美  你看入口…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.40,0:07:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.36,0:07:30.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是來見你的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.99,0:07:34.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放學後  我在那邊的公園等你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.30,0:07:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.77,0:07:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害啊  比呂美
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.39,0:07:50.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那個4號  競爭率很高的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.84,0:07:52.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧  很帥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.32,0:07:57.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說了  比呂美也很為難的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.72,0:08:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  這樣好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.79,0:08:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼好不好的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.07,0:08:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.96,0:08:08.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去廁所
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.33,0:08:19.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的啊  那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.68,0:08:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明不喜歡她…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.51,0:08:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我積蓄已久的感情…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.55,0:08:31.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  比呂美的心意…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.83,0:08:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果用真心來想像一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.20,0:08:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了比呂美  這是最好的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.03,0:08:42.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.31,0:08:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  和這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.65,0:08:54.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一郎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.25,0:08:57.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒  你有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.95,0:09:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.84,0:09:17.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在品嚐佳餚的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.89,0:09:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要表現得高興一點哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.03,0:09:23.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在的心情就和養雞場裡的雞一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.30,0:09:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如同必須不停地接受傳到眼前來的東西的心情…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.53,0:09:34.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對  你是像雷轟丸一般
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.63,0:09:37.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以天空為目標的特殊的雞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.69,0:09:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擁有自己意志的  特殊的雞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.12,0:09:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己的意志嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.07,0:09:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.02,0:09:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就直說了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.09,0:09:51.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在看見你  讓我腦子裡很混亂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.31,0:09:53.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫時別管我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.44,0:10:00.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到什麼時候？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.94,0:10:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.04,0:10:26.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前段時間我見過仲上真一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.93,0:10:29.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很喜歡我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.20,0:10:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仲上君說了什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.66,0:10:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.64,0:10:41.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我交往吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.98,0:10:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禮拜天下午一點  車站廣場
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.20,0:10:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提前考慮好想去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.27,0:10:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  請等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.71,0:10:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.80,0:10:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.80,0:11:00.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看樣子要下雪了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.74,0:11:04.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你討厭下雪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.97,0:11:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能騎摩托了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.18,0:11:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.60,0:11:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡  但也討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.21,0:11:18.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法對自己喜歡的事物直抒心意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.90,0:11:19.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很痛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.57,0:11:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.36,0:11:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我送你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.21,0:11:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真虧你能來到這個家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.34,0:11:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來告訴你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.79,0:12:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那天開始  我開始討厭起雪來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.40,0:12:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.28,0:12:26.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.50,0:12:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對4號說了些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.17,0:12:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要和他交往嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.17,0:12:35.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  定下了禮拜天的約會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.71,0:12:39.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  他已經提出來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.91,0:12:42.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  不是很好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.80,0:12:46.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多管閒事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.74,0:12:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿真  回來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.10,0:12:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她和別的男人一起回來的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.08,0:13:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些事  別故意說給我聽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.25,0:13:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姥姥  真一郎他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.25,0:13:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我暫時別管他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.25,0:13:30.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得很無聊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.11,0:13:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊  那條皮帶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.32,0:13:37.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真一郎的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.49,0:13:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.59,0:13:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是先寄存在我這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.01,0:13:46.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他對你說過什麼了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.51,0:13:49.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.90,0:13:51.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.37,0:13:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要出門嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.09,0:13:55.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約會
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.82,0:13:56.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.88,0:14:06.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好帥  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.54,0:14:09.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.06,0:14:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  是什麼類型的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.78,0:14:16.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可愛吧  是學校的學生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.78,0:14:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們學校的  湯淺比呂美
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.10,0:14:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說過  從老爸那裡拿到幫忙割稻子的錢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.67,0:14:34.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.53,0:14:37.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天  我送你件毛衣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.93,0:14:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.77,0:14:54.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  我還是第一次和男孩子一起看電影
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.54,0:14:57.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都是和乃繪看的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.49,0:14:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們關係很好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.44,0:15:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸和祖母都死了  母親出門上班
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.31,0:15:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都是我們倆一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.81,0:15:11.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的心情  我知道得很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.45,0:15:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包括她自己沒有注意到的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.89,0:15:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了吧  多不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.06,0:15:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了是我想買
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.61,0:15:32.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一共是7500日元
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.24,0:15:35.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  7500日元呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.57,0:15:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.41,0:15:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.65,0:15:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小愛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.23,0:15:43.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.60,0:15:48.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.44,0:15:50.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你用不著道歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.68,0:15:54.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得小愛更適合明亮的顏色
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.41,0:15:58.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一郎選的毛衣樸素了點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.93,0:16:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來你知道了  一起去購物的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.99,0:16:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有關係啦  只是購物而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.72,0:16:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.99,0:16:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那件毛衣不是真一郎選給我的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.82,0:16:20.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是我自作主張地買了真一郎碰過的那件
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.56,0:16:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一郎他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.13,0:16:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他喜歡的毛衣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.59,0:16:28.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自作主張地…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.77,0:16:37.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.44,0:16:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.30,0:16:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  果然我還是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.42,0:16:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個啊  有些事要你幫我傳達給仲上真一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.09,0:16:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫他快點決定乃繪的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.70,0:17:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們兩個會交往
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.00,0:17:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.64,0:17:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.56,0:17:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.52,0:17:53.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒  沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.82,0:17:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.60,0:17:57.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.66,0:18:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  你在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.49,0:18:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  馬上就結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.14,0:18:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又和男人一起回來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.55,0:18:31.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別人會說閒話的  你得再注意一點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.57,0:18:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家還有真一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.90,0:18:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是被別人以為我和一個放蕩女兒在一起生活
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.96,0:18:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不知道背地裡會被說些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.44,0:18:40.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.83,0:18:44.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼說那樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.90,0:18:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因為我是我媽媽的女兒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.54,0:18:52.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因為發生過那件事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.70,0:18:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就說我也很放蕩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.38,0:18:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把那些話都…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.13,0:19:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.80,0:19:02.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一刻也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.25,0:19:06.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之你給我注意點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.79,0:19:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這是做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.67,0:19:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿真
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.78,0:19:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那件事  指的是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.22,0:19:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和阿真你沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.59,0:19:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從很早就覺得了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.69,0:19:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽  你對比呂美是不是太過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.58,0:19:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一郎君  別這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.33,0:19:27.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.64,0:19:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算什麼算！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.78,0:19:31.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說算了  別管我了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.82,0:19:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比呂美
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.59,0:19:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽  求你了  你就別再…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.18,0:20:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽對你說了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.44,0:20:05.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那件事是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.25,0:20:09.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴你一件很不得了的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.10,0:20:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我出生的比較晚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.53,0:20:16.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以真一郎君是哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.18,0:20:21.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…什麼玩笑？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.20,0:20:24.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的像玩笑一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.57,0:20:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯母告訴我了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.70,0:20:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一郎君的父親  可能就是我真正的父親
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.10,0:20:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.87,0:21:17.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  真差勁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.25,0:21:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少女離去之處  積下一片水窪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.64,0:21:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少女之淚積下的水窪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.69,0:21:42.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知為何是那樣的幽深
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.74,0:21:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無盡的幽深
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.00,0:21:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我似乎就要被吸入那其中的深淵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.03,0:22:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一郎的頭頂有蟑螂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.73,0:22:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一郎的背上也有蟑螂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.21,0:23:44.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放棄…比呂美嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.47,0:23:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你向真一郎道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.31,0:23:50.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這女人  是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.69,0:23:54.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說清楚  然後寫在這裡
